parameters:
\SE[62]I didn't hear you say you wanted to go to Lunaroa's
place...

\SE[50]... I had a worse injury than you. \SE[74] But, I managed
to get treatment in time. \SE[75] I don't think there's any life-
threatening condition.
\SE[50]Maybe... Lunaroa... might not wake up anymore...

\SE[50]You appeared in my dream... and said, Because it's
pitiful, I'll let you meet her one last time...

\SE[31]If only I... were stronger... \SE[40]This wouldn't have...
happened...!!

\SE[64]L-Lunaroa, who fought seriously, got defeated...?
\SE[45]No matter who it was, it would have been impossible...

\SE[74]Let's try asking Cat... If there's a doctor knowledgeable
in magic and medicine... Maybe they'll know some way.

\SE[50]Don't rely too much on me. \SE[3]I can't just stand by
without doing something either.

\SE[50]Then go back to your room and get some rest. \!\SE[3]You
were seriously injured too.

\SE[76]Sigh... Well then, I'll go... \SE[75]Vita, please take
care of the two of them.
